                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> to <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span></p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The naval crew attacks as a disciplined whole against each enemy in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5], with a @Check[reflex|dc:23|basic] save. The damage depends on the number of actions. <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[(1d6+2)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(3d6+6)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(4d6+8)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>"
                },
