                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 3
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The naval crew draws, loads, and shoots its hand crossbows. The bolts hit in a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 60 feet that deals @Damage[5d6[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage with a @Check[reflex|dc:23|basic] save. When the naval crew is reduced to 2 or fewer segments, this area decreases to a @Template[type:burst|distance:5].</p>"
                },
